00:20:07,980 --> 00:20:09,220
 Which college is Kang Hu Yeong applying to? 

269
00:20:09,220 --> 00:20:12,110
 What's the point of knowing? You can't follow him there. 

270
00:20:12,110 --> 00:20:14,090
You chased him for three years, but it didn't work out.

271
00:20:14,090 --> 00:20:15,740
Just give it up.

272
00:20:15,740 --> 00:20:17,640
Yes.

273
00:20:18,790 --> 00:20:23,020
 Did you hear the girl from the liberal arts class got rejected? 

274
00:20:23,020 --> 00:20:25,500
 They made a fuss in the library. 

275
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:30,820
 It's because Hu Yeong has no interest in girls yet. 

276
00:20:30,820 --> 00:20:33,370
 We're growing up now. 

277
00:20:33,370 --> 00:20:37,470
 There will be more handsome guys than him. 

278
00:20:51,300 --> 00:20:54,300
You're the only one I told.

279
00:21:36,080 --> 00:21:38,280
Keep reading the comic book.

280
00:21:39,350 --> 00:21:42,380
You're more handsome than these guys. What can I do?

281
00:21:42,380 --> 00:21:45,290
I can't argue with that.

282
00:21:46,540 --> 00:21:49,630
I just remembered something huge,

283
00:21:49,630 --> 00:21:51,970
but I won't tell you.

284
00:21:51,970 --> 00:21:55,930
Tell me. What's so huge?

285
00:21:56,890 --> 00:21:58,140
I won't tell you.

286
00:21:58,140 --> 00:22:01,100
- What is it? 
 - I won't tell you.

287
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:03,530
You won't? You won't?

288
00:22:03,530 --> 00:22:07,710
- You won't? 
 - It tickles! Stop!

289
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:12,500
I love you, Lee Hong Ju.

290
00:22:13,910 --> 00:22:15,760
Me, too.

291
00:22:16,940 --> 00:22:18,640
Why do you laugh?

292
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:48,580
It's snowing.

293
00:22:48,580 --> 00:22:50,710
Wow!

294
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:53,480
It's pretty.

295
00:22:59,800 --> 00:23:01,600
Kang Hu Yeong?

296
00:23:02,700 --> 00:23:04,490
Kang Hu Yeong?

297
00:23:10,380 --> 00:23:13,610
Wont you ask me to come in?

298
00:23:14,910 --> 00:23:16,980
Please come in.

299
00:23:50,380 --> 00:23:54,390
There's nothing to drink at home. Is that okay?

300
00:23:55,730 --> 00:23:58,890
I also don't have much time.

301
00:23:58,890 --> 00:24:00,970
So…

302
00:24:02,010 --> 00:24:05,940
I prepared this in a little hurry.

303
00:24:07,030 --> 00:24:08,400
This is…

304
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:12,880
I'm sure it's better than what you expected.

305
00:24:19,250 --> 00:24:22,620
