00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:31,570
   

443
00:36:31,570 --> 00:36:40,420
♫  Did we get reunited by coincidence?  ♫

444
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:50,830
♫  The days we spent like that  ♫

445
00:36:50,830 --> 00:36:57,630
♫  Was it a coincidence?  ♫

446
00:36:57,630 --> 00:37:09,900
♫  I hope that you, whom I'm looking at, will look at me, too  ♫

447
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:23,400
♫  I hope you come a bit closer to my heart now  ♫

