00:38:03,230 --> 00:38:06,790
He doesn't have class, but why won't he reply?

451
00:38:17,390 --> 00:38:22,310
You should have started preparing if you heard the inspectors were coming.

452
00:38:22,310 --> 00:38:25,090
What will they think of our school?

453
00:38:25,090 --> 00:38:29,130
They'll know we've been rushing after being notified.

454
00:38:29,130 --> 00:38:31,480
Seriously.

455
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:34,810
Wow, am I really in a relationship?

456
00:38:34,810 --> 00:38:37,080
Why do I feel lonelier?

457
00:38:39,100 --> 00:38:40,910
You're so clumsy.

458
00:38:40,910 --> 00:38:43,100
 How could you miss that? 

459
00:38:43,100 --> 00:38:45,060
 Are you okay? 

460
00:38:59,610 --> 00:39:03,320
I told her so many times not to wear shoes like those.

461
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:06,460
Seriously. Gosh.

462
00:39:06,460 --> 00:39:08,580
Why right here?

463
00:39:08,580 --> 00:39:12,350
Who's going to marry her, anyway?

464
00:39:29,790 --> 00:39:33,280
Everyone will find out about our secret relationship at this rate.

465
00:39:35,130 --> 00:39:37,360
Hye Ji,

466
00:39:37,360 --> 00:39:39,810
you'd better be ready from now on.

467
00:39:39,810 --> 00:39:41,430
Pardon?

468
00:39:43,540 --> 00:39:48,790
I decided not to hide my feelings in front of anyone.

469
00:39:52,950 --> 00:39:55,780
That's what I've wanted to hear.

470
00:40:00,370 --> 00:40:02,100
Father.

471
00:40:12,240 --> 00:40:15,200
I will take Hye Ji with me.

472
00:40:16,850 --> 00:40:19,750
She's my daughter. How dare you?

473
00:40:24,120 --> 00:40:27,180
Hurry and take her with you, Son-in-law.

474
00:40:27,180 --> 00:40:29,120
Yes!

475
00:40:30,590 --> 00:40:33,770
What? Really? Did everyone know?

476
00:40:33,770 --> 00:40:39,230
We have his approval. We have his approval, Teacher Kim!

477
00:40:42,610 --> 00:40:45,030
Vice Principal.

478
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:51,620
Here is the food you ordered.

479
00:40:53,090 --> 00:40:56,250
- Excuse me, here you go. 
 - Thank you.

480
00:40:56,250 --> 00:40:58,540
Enjoy.

481
00:41:04,380 --> 00:41:07,620
- Welcome! 
